title: Jeuru - Couldn’t Be (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Jeuru performing “Couldn’t Be” live at Dypång, in Aarhus, Denmark, during SPOT Festival in May 2022.

Jeuru - Vocals
Kasper Bengtsen - Guitar
Columbus Grønlund - Keys
Valdemar Weile - Drums

Recording Engineers: Jonna Aspeklev & Rasmus Bredvig
Mix Engineer: Rasmus Bredvig at Tapetown / Lydhavnen
Assistant Mix engineer: Jonna Aspeklev
Mastering: Emil Thomsen at ET Mastering / Lydhavnen
Cameras: Claus Haargaard, Torsten Frøstrup, Christian Daugaard & Charlee Aurora
Production & Camera Assists: Charlina Mikkelsen, Juliane Eickstädt, Max Bülow Lassen, Asbjørn Lyhne, Søren Flecks & Morten Lovechild
Video Post Production/Edit: Rasmus Bredvig

KEXP at SPOT Festival was made possible by Music Export Denmark, SPOT Festival and ROSA, and with the kind support of the Danish Arts Foundation, the Ministry of Foreign Affairs of Denmark and the Ministry of Culture, Denmark.
